=== 国际邀请赛 ===
[[File:The_International_2015,_Key_Arena,_Seattle,_Washington_D.C..jpg|300px]]
为了让更多的DOTA玩家接受Dota 2，并展现游戏的新性能，在2011年，Valve发起了[[DOTA2国际邀请赛|DOTA2国际邀请赛]]（简称TI）这一Dota 2领域的[[电子竞技|电子竞技]]锦标赛，并提供高达100万美元的奖金，邀请世界各地的共16組顶级战队参加。<ref>{{cite web |last=Reilly |first=Jim |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/08/01/valve-goes-big-with-dota-2-tournament |title=Valve Goes Big with Dota 2 Tournament |date=August 1, 2011 |publisher=IGN |archivedate=2012-11-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109072431/http://www.ign.com/articles/2011/08/01/valve-goes-big-with-dota-2-tournament |accessdate=2016-10-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>随后，TI国际邀请赛际成为了每年一度的冠军锦标赛，举办地点也迁到了美国华盛顿州的[[西雅图|西雅图]]市（第一届在德国科隆）。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/04/25/dota-2-the-international-3-announced/ |title= Dota 2: The International 3 announced |first= TJ |last= Hafer |date= April 25, 2013 |publisher= [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |accessdate= August 15, 2013 |archive-date= 2013-08-13 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130813060925/http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/04/25/dota-2-the-international-3-announced/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>到了2013年，第三届国际邀请赛的奖金池通过互动指南的销售超过了280万美元，超过了此前[[英雄联盟|英雄联盟]]第二季锦标赛的记录，成为电子竞技历史上最大的奖金池。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/dota-2s-the-international-3-reaches-2m-prize-pool/1100-6408442/ | title = Dota 2's The International 3 reaches $2m prize pool | last = Gaston | first = Martin | publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | date = May 16, 2013 | accessdate = 2016-10-14 | archive-date = 2013-11-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131118055918/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/dota-2s-the-international-3-reaches-2m-prize-pool/1100-6408442/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.joystiq.com/2013/08/04/dota-2-international-begins-prize-pool-over-2-8-million/ | title = The International 3 begins, Prize pool of over $2.8 million | date = August 4, 2013 | first = Thomas | last = Schulenberg | work = Joystiq | accessdate = August 15, 2013 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130807002328/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/08/04/dota-2-international-begins-prize-pool-over-2-8-million | archive-date = 2013-08-07 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>互动指南是一个可选的但必须单独购买的虚拟物品，V社将该收入的25%直接用于比赛奖金。<ref>{{cite web|title=Introducing the Interactive Compendium|url=http://blog.dota2.com/2013/05/introducing-the-interactive-compendium/|website=Dota 2|accessdate=July 7, 2016|archive-date=2016-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811043833/http://blog.dota2.com/2013/05/introducing-the-interactive-compendium/|dead-url=no}}</ref>从此，每年国际邀请赛的奖金池都会打破上一届比赛奖金池的记录。第四届国际邀请赛（2014年）的奖金池已达到1090万美元，超过了[[超级碗|超级碗]]、[[美国高尔夫巡回赛|美国高尔夫巡回赛]]和[[环法自行车赛|环法自行车赛]]。<ref>{{cite web | last = Newhouse | first = Alex | url = http://www.gamespot.com/articles/10-million-dota-2-international-exceeds-super-bowl-masters-and-tour-de-france-prizes/1100-6420785/ | title = $10 Million Dota 2 International Exceeds Super Bowl, Masters, and Tour de France Prizes | date = June 27, 2014 | accessdate = October 12, 2015 | publisher = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archive-date = 2015-10-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151004070022/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/10-million-dota-2-international-exceeds-super-bowl-masters-and-tour-de-france-prizes/1100-6420785/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>2015年至2019年，国际邀请赛的奖金池分别超过了1840万美元、2077万美元、2478万美元、2500万美元、3330万美元，分别使当年冠军队伍{{flagicon|USA}}'''Evil Geniuses'''、{{flagicon|China}}'''Wings'''、{{flagicon|EU}}'''Team Liquid'''、{{flagicon|EU}}'''OG'''战队收获超过600万美元、913万美元、1090万美元、1119万美元、1560万美元的奖金（其中OG战队连续获得2018年、2019年冠军）。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.pcgamer.com/the-international-2015-prize-distribution-announced/ |title= The International 2015 prize distribution announced |date= July 21, 2015 |accessdate= July 21, 2015 |work= PC Gamer |author= Phil Savage |archive-date= 2015-07-23 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150723150749/http://www.pcgamer.com/the-international-2015-prize-distribution-announced/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Daultrey|first1=Stephen|title=Pakistani teenager becomes youngest gamer to surpass $1million in eSports earnings as Dota 2 tournament sets major records|url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2015/8/pakistani-gamer-becomes-youngest-gamer-to-surpass-1million-in-esports-earnings-a-391494|publisher=[[Guinness_World_Records|Guinness World Records]]|accessdate=September 5, 2015|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905093119/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/2015/8/pakistani-gamer-becomes-youngest-gamer-to-surpass-1million-in-esports-earnings-a-391494|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.dota2.com/international/overview/ | title= Dota 2 - The International | accessdate= Dec 19, 2016 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20171204084812/http://www.dota2.com/international/overview/ | archive-date= 2017-12-04 | dead-url= yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Pro video gamers are making millions by age 30 in the booming world of 'esports'|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2018/10/03/esports-pro-video-gamers-are-making-millions-by-age-30-and-retiring.html|accessdate=2019-06-22|date=2018-10-03|last=Choudhury|first=Arjun Kharpal,Saheli Roy|work=CNBC|language=en|archive-date=2018-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004103904/https://www.cnbc.com/2018/10/03/esports-pro-video-gamers-are-making-millions-by-age-30-and-retiring.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

随着国际邀请赛的举行，若干电子竞技赛事开始从Dota过渡到Dota2，其中包括ESWC<ref>{{cite web |last=Strisland |first=Jonas |url=http://www.cadred.org/News/Article/160351/ |title=ESWC: DotA 2 Final |date=October 25, 2011 |publisher=[[Cadred|Cadred]] |archivedate=2012-06-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120605071206/http://www.cadred.org/News/Article/160351/ |accessdate=2016-10-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。Dota 2测试期的第一年结束时，它已成为排名第二的付费游戏，仅次于[[星海爭霸II：自由之翼|星际争霸II]]。<ref>{{cite web |last=Macdonald |first=Stuart |url=http://www.sk-gaming.com/content/36218-PGT_outlines_best_paying_games_of_2011 |title=PGT outlines best paying games of 2011 |date=January 7, 2012 |publisher=[[SK_Gaming|SK Gaming]] |archivedate=2012-05-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120528033009/http://www.sk-gaming.com/content/36218-PGT_outlines_best_paying_games_of_2011 |accessdate=2016-10-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
在2012年，Dota 2正式成为世界电子竞技大赛（[[WCG|WCG]]）的比赛项目。<ref>{{cite web |first=Ulrich |last=Hanten |url=http://www.gosugamers.net/dota/news/21851-wcg-2012-dota-and-dota-2-groups-drawn |title=WCG 2012: DotA and Dota 2 groups drawn |publisher=Gosu Gamers |date=December 2012 |accessdate=March 3, 2013 |archive-date=2013-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130303165120/http://www.gosugamers.net/dota/news/21851-wcg-2012-dota-and-dota-2-groups-drawn |dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年，电子竞技联盟（ESL）开始为其举办季度性的锦标赛，称为RaidCall EMS One，它同时也是是2013年年初最大型的dota2独立赛事。<ref>{{cite web |last=Savage |first=Phil |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/01/28/esl-announce-the-largest-independent-dota-2-competition-so-far/ |title=ESL announce the largest independent Dota 2 competition so far |date=January 28, 2013 |publisher=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |accessdate=March 3, 2013 |archive-date=2013-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130303165411/http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/01/28/esl-announce-the-largest-independent-dota-2-competition-so-far/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2013年九月初，中国电子竞技协会举办了Dota 2锦标赛——WPC-ACE Dota 2 in 2013。这项赛事是电子竞技历史上奖金额度第三高的比赛，也是国际邀请赛之外奖金额度最大的比赛。<ref>{{cite web | last = Nordmark | first = Sam | url = http://www.ongamers.com/articles/dk-win-wpc-ace-league/1100-525/ | title = DK win WPC-ACE League! | date = January 1, 2014 | publisher = [[onGamers|onGamers]] | accessdate = January 27, 2014 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140203022353/http://www.ongamers.com/articles/dk-win-wpc-ace-league/1100-525/ | archivedate = 2014-02-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>2013年6月12号，在电子娱乐博览会上，Nexon宣布投资20亿韩元（大致170万美元）举办一个面向业余玩家和职业玩家的联赛。<ref>{{cite web | last = Horton | first = Samuel | url = http://www.sk-gaming.com/content/318043-Nexon_to_invest_17_million_in_Dota_2 | title = Nexon to invest $1.7 million in Dota 2 | date = June 13, 2012 | publisher = [[SK_Gaming|SK Gaming]] | accessdate = 2016-10-14 | archive-date = 2013-09-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130916133523/http://www.sk-gaming.com/content/318043-Nexon_to_invest_17_million_in_Dota_2 | dead-url = no }}</ref>互动指南曾是国际邀请赛的专属，但从2014年的ASUS ROG梦幻联赛开始，Valve允许第三方组织的比赛售卖互动指南。<ref>{{cite web | last = Bailey | first = Matthew | url = http://www.ongamers.com/articles/the-asus-rog-dreamleague-will-be-the-first-tournament-supported-by-a-third-party-compendium/1100-937/ | title = The ASUS ROG DreamLeague will be the first tournament supported by a third party Compendium | date = February 26, 2014 | publisher = [[onGamers|onGamers]] | accessdate = October 12, 2015 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140306173541/http://www.ongamers.com/articles/the-asus-rog-dreamleague-will-be-the-first-tournament-supported-by-a-third-party-compendium/1100-937 | archivedate = 2014-03-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>2015年，Dota 2亚洲邀请赛在上海举行，通过互动指南的销售，本次比赛的奖金池突破了三百万美元。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Strom|first1=Steven|title=The Eastern International|url=http://www.redbull.com/us/en/esports/stories/1331698729388/the-dota-2-asia-championships|website=Red Bull|accessdate=July 12, 2016|archive-date=2016-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216043813/http://www.redbull.com/us/en/esports/stories/1331698729388/the-dota-2-asia-championships|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Bester|first1=Alan|title=The Great Chinese Collapse of the Shanghai Major|url=http://espn.go.com/esports/story/_/id/14897064/the-great-chinese-collapse-shanghai-major|website=ESPN|accessdate=July 12, 2016|archive-date=2016-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160703225038/http://espn.go.com/esports/story/_/id/14897064/the-great-chinese-collapse-shanghai-major|dead-url=no}}</ref>此後[[完美世界_(公司)|完美世界]]又在上海舉辦多屆Dota 2亚洲邀请赛<ref name=上海/>。到2016年6月为止，Dota 2已成为盈利最高的电子竞技游戏。据统计，专业级的Dota 2锦标赛的奖金总计已达到6500万美元，将近英雄联盟锦标赛的两倍。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fossett|first1=Wyatt|title=How Videogames Became a Sport, and Why They're Here to Stay (Hint: Money!)|url=https://techvibes.com/2016/06/21/how-videogames-became-a-sport-and-why-theyre-here-to-stay-hint-money|website=Tech Vibes|accessdate=15 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160710183703/https://techvibes.com/2016/06/21/how-videogames-became-a-sport-and-why-theyre-here-to-stay-hint-money|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== DOTA特锦赛 ===
2015年开始，Valve开始举办季节性的规模稍小一些的锦标赛，称为特锦赛<ref name="Majors">{{cite web|last1=Sykes|first1=Tom|title=Dota 2 Major Championships announced|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/dota-2-major-championships-announced/|website=PC Gamer|accessdate=June 14, 2016|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402081538/http://www.pcgamer.com/dota-2-major-championships-announced/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ign.com/articles/2015/04/25/valve-announces-the-dota-2-major-championships|title=Valve Announces The Dota 2 Major Championships|first=Mitch|last=Dyer|website=[[IGN|IGN]]|date=April 24, 2015|accessdate=November 15, 2015|archive-date=2015-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151118053735/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/04/25/valve-announces-the-dota-2-major-championships|dead-url=no}}</ref>，每季的奖池有300万美元。锦标赛的原型基于同样出于V社的[[第一人称射击游戏|第一人称射击游戏]]——[[反恐精英：全球攻势|反恐精英：全球攻势]]。第一个特锦赛由[[ESL|ESL]]于2015年11月11日～21日在德国法兰克福举办，冠军是OG战队<ref>{{cite web|last1=Porter|first1=Matt|title=Dota 2 Major Announced for Frankfurt|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/09/24/dota-2-major-announced-for-frankfurt|website=IGN|accessdate=13 October 2016|archive-date=2016-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160906000505/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/09/24/dota-2-major-announced-for-frankfurt|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Strom|first1=Steven|title=$3 Million Dota 2 Tournament Ends With an Upset and an Announcement|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/11/22/3-million-dota-2-tournament-ends-with-an-upset-and-an-announcement|website=IGN|accessdate=13 October 2016|archive-date=2016-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111110424/http://www.ign.com/articles/2015/11/22/3-million-dota-2-tournament-ends-with-an-upset-and-an-announcement|dead-url=no}}</ref>；接下来的特锦赛由[[完美世界|完美世界]]于2016年3月2日～6日在上海梅赛德斯奔驰中心举办，冠军是Team Secret战队<ref>{{cite web|last1=Thursten|first1=Chris|title=Valve have announced the Dota 2 Shanghai Major|url=http://www.pcgamer.com/valve-have-announced-the-dota-2-shanghai-major/|website=PC Gamer|accessdate=December 1, 2015|archive-date=2015-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125012638/http://www.pcgamer.com/valve-have-announced-the-dota-2-shanghai-major/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Lee|first1=Timothy|title=Team Secret defeats Team Liquid to win the Dota 2 Shanghai Major 2016|url=http://espn.go.com/esports/story/_/id/14914913/team-secret-defeats-team-liquid-win-dota-2-shanghai-major-2016-esports|website=ESPN|accessdate=July 7, 2016|archive-date=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160702094455/http://espn.go.com/esports/story/_/id/14914913/team-secret-defeats-team-liquid-win-dota-2-shanghai-major-2016-esports|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第三个也是在国际邀请赛之前的特锦赛由PGL在2016年6月于[[马尼拉|马尼拉]]举办,这次OG战队再次夺得冠军。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Cocke|first1=Taylor|title=OG wins Manila, becomes first team to win two Dota 2 majors|url=https://esports.yahoo.com/og-wins-manila-becomes-first-team-to-win-two-dota-2-majors-192854222.html|website=esports.yahoo.com|publisher=Yahoo|accessdate=June 14, 2016|archive-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629021317/https://esports.yahoo.com/og-wins-manila-becomes-first-team-to-win-two-dota-2-majors-192854222.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
在这样的新制度下，国际邀请赛被大家视为“夏季锦标赛”。第六届国际邀请赛（TI6）是在新形式下的第一届。<ref name="Majors"/><ref>{{cite web|last1=Sutterlin|first1=Alan|title=The postive impact of Valve's Majors format on the Dota 2 esports scene|url=http://espn.go.com/esports/story/_/id/14668735/the-positive-impact-valve-majors-format-dota-2-esports-scene|website=ESPN|accessdate=June 27, 2016|archive-date=2016-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421001024/http://espn.go.com/esports/story/_/id/14668735/the-positive-impact-valve-majors-format-dota-2-esports-scene|dead-url=no}}</ref>TI6沿用了之前的销售互动指南的众筹模式，也使得它再一次刷新了电子竞技历史上的奖池记录——2000万美元，这次的冠军是Wings战队。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Albert|first1=Brian|title=Dota 2's $20 Million International Starts Today|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/08/03/dota-2s-20-million-international-starts-today|website=IGN|accessdate=4 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160805035535/http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/08/03/dota-2s-20-million-international-starts-today|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Erzberger|first1=Tyler|title=Teenage captain leads esports team to $9.1 million prize|url=http://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/17296935/teenage-captain-leads-esports-team-91-million-prize|website=ESPN|accessdate=14 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815070147/http://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/17296935/teenage-captain-leads-esports-team-91-million-prize|dead-url=no}}</ref>在这次的玩家见面会上，Valve宣布由于赛事过于密集，在下来他们将把赛事的数量从原先的三个降低到两个。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Van Allen|first1=Eric|title=Valve plans to reduce number of majors in 2017|url=http://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/17194814/valve-plans-reduce-number-majors-2017|website=ESPN|accessdate=6 August 2016|archive-date=2016-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160806105039/http://www.espn.com/esports/story/_/id/17194814/valve-plans-reduce-number-majors-2017|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Good|first1=Owen|title=Dota 2's second championship season begins with The Boston Major|url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/10/4/13160996/dota-2s-second-championship-season-begins-with-the-boston-major|website=Polygon|accessdate=5 October 2016|archive-date=2016-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005123421/http://www.polygon.com/2016/10/4/13160996/dota-2s-second-championship-season-begins-with-the-boston-major|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== DOTA职业巡回赛 ===
在2017年第七届国际邀请赛后，由于受到玩家和各战队对于国际邀请赛直接邀请参赛队伍不透明的批评，Valve宣布将用新的Dota职业巡回赛系统（DPC）来取代以往的特锦赛模式。在职业巡回赛模式下，各支队伍需要通过参加Valve赞助的各项赛事来赚取积分，到赛季末时将根据积分情况来决定接下来的国际邀请赛直接邀请参赛队伍。在2018-19赛季，职业巡回赛排名前12的队伍将会直接受邀参加国际邀请赛。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Dota 2 - The Road to The International|url=http://www.dota2.com/majorsminors/|accessdate=2019-06-22|work=Dota2.com|archive-date=2019-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190622030905/http://www.dota2.com/majorsminors/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

